# Add Treasure Card Contents (Rương) Drag-and-Drop Editor

When editing/creating an adventure card of type `treasure`, show a drag-and-drop card picker (reusing [CardDeckBuilder](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/maps/CardDeckBuilder.tsx#23-79) from maps refactoring) to select the cards contained in the treasure chest.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend

#### [MODIFY] [AdventureCard.ts](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/server/src/models/AdventureCard.ts)

Add `contents` field — array of AdventureCard ObjectId references:

```diff
+ contents?: mongoose.Types.ObjectId[];  // interface
+ contents: [{ type: Schema.Types.ObjectId, ref: 'AdventureCard' }]  // schema
```

#### [MODIFY] [gameData.ts (validator)](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/server/src/validators/gameData.ts)

Add `contents: z.array(z.string()).optional()` to `createAdventureCardSchema`.

#### [MODIFY] [adventureCardController.ts](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/server/src/controllers/adventureCardController.ts)

Populate `contents` with card data when returning adventure cards (`.populate('contents')`).

---

### Frontend Types

#### [MODIFY] [gameDataService.ts](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/services/gameDataService.ts)

Add `contents?: AdventureCard[]` to the [AdventureCard](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/services/gameDataService.ts#33-63) interface.

---

### Frontend Components

#### [MODIFY] [AdventureCardEditForm.tsx](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/adventureCards/AdventureCardEditForm.tsx)

- Add `allCards: AdventureCard[]` prop
- When `card.type === 'treasure'`, render [CardDeckBuilder](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/maps/CardDeckBuilder.tsx#23-79) with:
  - `cardIds` = `form.contents` (mapped to IDs)
  - `onDeckChange` → update `form.contents`
  - `deckLabel="🎁 Rương (nội dung rương)"`

#### [MODIFY] [AdventureCardEditModal.tsx](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/adventureCards/AdventureCardEditModal.tsx)

- Add `allCards: AdventureCard[]` prop, pass to [AdventureCardEditForm](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/adventureCards/AdventureCardEditForm.tsx#40-270)

#### [MODIFY] [AdventureCardCreateModal.tsx](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/adventureCards/AdventureCardCreateModal.tsx)

- Add `allCards: AdventureCard[]` prop
- When `type === 'treasure'`, render [CardDeckBuilder](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/maps/CardDeckBuilder.tsx#23-79)

#### [MODIFY] [AdventureCards.tsx](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/pages/AdventureCards.tsx)

- Pass `cards` (all cards) to both [AdventureCardEditModal](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/adventureCards/AdventureCardEditModal.tsx#40-151) and [AdventureCardCreateModal](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/adventureCards/AdventureCardCreateModal.tsx#60-361) as `allCards`

#### [MODIFY] [useAdventureCardEdit.ts](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/adventureCards/useAdventureCardEdit.ts)

- In [handleSaveCard](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/adventureCards/useAdventureCardEdit.ts#198-223), map `form.contents` from `AdventureCard[]` → `string[]` (IDs) before sending to API

