Remove the duplicate [getCardImageUrl](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/maps/mapUtils.ts#72-78) — import [getAdventureCardImageUrl](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/adventureCards/adventureCardUtils.ts#49-55) from `adventureCardUtils` instead. Update [CardDeckBuilder](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/maps/CardDeckBuilder.tsx#23-79) default prop to use [getAdventureCardImageUrl](file:///c:/Users/inter/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/TeyvatCardGameBackend/admin-web/src/components/adventureCards/adventureCardUtils.ts#49-55).

